Author: Blythe King [aut, cre], Haoran Yan [aut], Laura Baracaldo [aut], Mengyang Gu [aut]
Maintainer: Blythe King <blyking@gmail.com>
Description: 
  Functions for performing fast Gaussian process-based segmentation of microscopy images using spatial smoothing and data-driven thresholding.
  Code based on Baracaldo, L., King, B., Yan, H., Lin, Y., Miolane, N., & Gu, M. (2025). 
  Unsupervised cell segmentation by fast Gaussian Processes. 
  arXiv preprint <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2505.18902>.
